---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Cookie Policy | Tech Aluminum" description="Tech Aluminum cookie policy — which cookies and local storage this website uses and why." lang="en">
  <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <div class="container"><ol>
      <li><a href="/en/">Home</a></li>
      <li aria-current="page">Cookie Policy</li>
    </ol></div>
  </nav>

  <section style="padding:5rem 0;background:var(--warm-white);">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:760px;">
      <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>
      <p style="color:var(--ink-soft);font-size:0.9rem;">Last updated: June 2026</p>

      <h2>1. About this policy</h2>
      <p>This policy explains how this website (techaluminum.com) uses cookies and similar local-storage technologies. By using the site you agree to the use described below. We keep this to the minimum required to make the site work.</p>

      <h2>2. We do not track you</h2>
      <p>Tech Aluminum does not use advertising cookies, third-party analytics, tracking pixels, or social-media tracking. We do not build visitor profiles and we do not sell or share any browsing data.</p>

      <h2>3. What we do store</h2>
      <ul style="line-height:1.8;color:var(--ink-soft);">
        <li><strong>Cookie-consent flag</strong> (local storage) — remembers that you have dismissed the cookie notice so it is not shown on every visit. Strictly functional.</li>
        <li><strong>Language preference</strong> — if set, remembers whether you are viewing the English, German, French or Italian version of the site.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>These are stored in your browser's local storage, contain no personal data, and are never transmitted to a third party.</p>

      <h2>4. Third-party requests</h2>
      <p>The site loads web fonts from Google Fonts to render typography, and our enquiry form is processed by Web3Forms to deliver your message to us by email. These providers receive only the data necessary to perform that function (your IP for font delivery; the form contents you submit). Neither sets advertising cookies through this site.</p>

      <h2>5. Managing cookies</h2>
      <p>You can clear local storage and cookies at any time through your browser settings. Because we use only strictly functional storage, clearing it will not break the site — you will simply see the cookie notice again.</p>

      <h2>6. Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about this policy: <a href="mailto:noel@techaluminum.com">noel@techaluminum.com</a> · <a href="https://wa.me/353871187806" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp</a>. See also our <a href="/en/privacy-policy/">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
